headline: Piper Sandler Raises IDEXX Laboratories (IDXX) PT to $700, Cites Strong Q2 Results
summary: IDEXX Laboratories Inc. (NASDAQ:IDXX) is one of the best performing S&P 500 stocks to buy now. On August 11, Piper Sandler raised the firm’s price target on Idexx Laboratories to $700 from $510 following the company’s Q2 2025 financial results. The firm kept a Neutral rating on the shares.
